<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="34" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="34">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="34">Body piceous with green brassy reflections. Elytral surface smooth, striae reduced to basal third, impunctate, 4 setiferous punctures on interval 3, stria 2 absent. Profemur glabrous. Abdominal sternum VII with 5+5 setiferous punctures.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
